name: Anaerobic into Sweet Spot
description:
Along with challenging your fitness by going from a short Anaerobic effort into a sustained Tempo effort, this session adds to that adaptation by including a large difference in cadence. Complete the opening low cadence Anaerobic Interval out of the seat, before settling into a high cadence tempo Interval.
